{"tid":2026244,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"買SE2既人真係好可憐","createTime":"2020-05-20T23:03:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T13:50:35.000Z","uid":219147,"like":11,"dislike":122,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b78f4b9325d683c14276ba23156909faec428a12","tid":2026244,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T23:03:43.000Z","msg":"其實應該話買蘋果既人真係好可憐 <br />\n（包括我自己）<br />\n1，人人戴口罩 SE2有touchid真係好方便好好用<br />\n所以你哋要選擇iphone SE2<br />\n答案錯：係蘋果冇張屏下指紋技術放係最新既iphone 呀..儍仔 ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買咗SE2既你哋 其實係間接幫蘋果數錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2，成皮野買部最新iphone 連最基本既屏下指紋技術都冇都算啦 連粒最新既A13都要分享埋比部垃圾SE2上面 <br />\n仲要係一前一後切肉式咁分開賣 咁叫咩做旗艦手機？一係你就一早講明就唔同 呢家好似比蘋果玩緊咁 因為SE2所以..連個二手價都爭啲比蘋果玩林埋 <br />\n吊你老母死蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f968e0a926c1879042adc7788f34817e250fcd","tid":2026244,"uid":46814,"like":112,"dislike":3,"score":109,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T23:09:40.000Z","msg":"你個中文老師都好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b28a971b2f60d0f771d24215a0f1523204c03b","tid":2026244,"uid":810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T23:11:26.000Z","msg":"成皮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb63a0d1fa242b9c131582b9d3494944d16a730","tid":2026244,"uid":242998,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T23:13:05.000Z","msg":"你的中文令人覺得很尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aea967d699dc5bf8d38e6bdcf6ab3b4befa48d5","tid":2026244,"uid":219147,"like":2,"dislike":81,"score":-79,"quote":{"pid":"f2f968e0a926c1879042adc7788f34817e250fcd","tid":2026244,"uid":46814,"like":112,"dislike":3,"score":109,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T23:09:40.000Z","msg